element.name: Uisce by Windsockers, Traditional Cache (1/1.5)

long-description.p:
In past years when houses did not have their own water supply there were many pumps such as these situated along the streets of Rush.
There is a plan for them to be restored back to their former glory at at some stage.
This is a simple cache and dash but care needs to be taken as the location is beside a very busy road .

element.encoded-hints: in the mouth of the beast!
